title: Logo Design - I need an artist!
body:
Hi Summoners,

I am looking for an artist that has experience in logo design.
I am looking to create a network and need an artist that can deliver multiple graphics.
You have no requirements except what you deliver!

If your work meets and/or exceeds criteria I will offer money for your work.

Please add me in-game @ bollockz or on Skype @ helloyesiamson

Cheers

replies.body:
Sent you a friend request in-game dude.
I can send you some of my work if you'd like, MrMunster is the IGN.
I don't do logo design myself but I know a few people who do. If you tell me what you want, I can forward it to them and if they're willing they can send you like a demo or something.
